				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>I feel that I should say something as everyone else has. Except that I don&#8217;t really mind much: the opinions below are not strongly held. </p>
<p>&#8211; I am somewhat nervous about a shorter word limit, and would prefer a longer one if we change it around a bit.</p>
<p>&#8211; I like the idea of everyone being on the same word limit for similar reasons to parfles (everyone working on the same challenge and the variety that is generated), but also agree that this could be quite flexible. Maybe the range of the word limit should be defined as 50 on either side &#8211; 200 to 300, so we can be sure that the parameters aren&#8217;t squishing creativity rather than challenging it?</p>
<p>That&#8217;s all for now.</p>
